metadata.name: Neon Hex Tiles #1
metadata.description:
The genesis piece by Pix3lboy in the Neon Tiles collection.

This unique work uses tiles of 6 x 6 hexagons in a neon palette which gives it a futuristic feel.

Generated in high resolution using modern technology including p5.js, this work is best seen in full screen.

5208 x 5208 px
